{"tid":1422080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"下一批福建幫打人有錢收，上面吹大雞","createTime":"2019-08-06T09:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T09:57:26.000Z","uid":35077,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0b8dff0ce1329e6e85148e5c64c2cd4d59dea7fd","tid":1422080,"uid":35077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:45:12.000Z","msg":"朋友第一手資料，有個大陸客係福建幫。<br />\n<br />\n1) 5/8 北角+荃灣係潺仔，只係叔父去快閃為影相先會走佬<br />\n2) 5/8 係冇錢收<br />\n3) 之後有可能會有錢收，係福建幫啲人啲大佬課金，每人 ~$2000<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">4) 上面福建可以有成千條村嘅人落嚟，啲仔、孫好壯，上面村同村之間唔同派打交都打得好癲</span><br />\n5) 唔少呢啲落嚟嘅人都係老竇老母落過嚟香港(抵壘?)，之後撈唔掂先返上去，呢啲人因為單程證仔女終審案攞到香港 *** 身份證喺香港做嘢<br />\n<br />\n大家小心，盡量著齊啲護具。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8PNZmv3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8PNZmv3.png&h=5687517a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X4dqg4s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX4dqg4s.png&h=8d702c34&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca5830947d6ea58cfe223730b5188f12b103409e","tid":1422080,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:46:42.000Z","msg":"嘩好驚 入南邊圍避一避先"},{"pid":"cd9af27aa5d4ccf10905034c76d514303bd5c038","tid":1422080,"uid":106290,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:47:39.000Z","msg":"叫埋福建中學啲人出嚟啦"},{"pid":"0a64c01cd8f23775ce7d2b049fc811059b4f69fa","tid":1422080,"uid":241468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:48:54.000Z","msg":"點報名啊 有2千蚊收咁好 問下你個fd pm我俾個報名方法黎"},{"pid":"035ff70b35b47b0b5c84f8aff9f5fd4839cf153a","tid":1422080,"uid":262032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:49:35.000Z","msg":"notes"},{"pid":"ed7d3f5b83975a0c3e59ea3627ea0a49b18cfee6","tid":1422080,"uid":262032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:49:49.000Z","msg":"*noted"},{"pid":"93ce9f8fc91c864cb28f613bfa0bceaba36fb4dc","tid":1422080,"uid":765,